{"tid":1679064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【猶差站起來了】史上第二次 香港半島酒店開放民眾避難","createTime":"2019-10-28T03:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T04:00:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f969c8313b07979740a4feea713668e618762863","tid":1679064,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/crfB0r3HvvPTIRH7V2gh4w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/6hxSucwjhsqH53h6zd6CcA--~B/dz0wO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/cb54ca0b1009aab18b62ce4c71ef4401\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FcrfB0r3HvvPTIRH7V2gh4w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6hxSucwjhsqH53h6zd6CcA--~B%2Fdz0wO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fcb54ca0b1009aab18b62ce4c71ef4401&h=835c6576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動持續，昨（27日）下午示威者於尖沙咀梳士巴利道發起「追究警暴」集會，不久就再度爆發警民衝突，警方投擲多枚催淚彈，許多民眾衝進香港半島酒店避難。<br />\n<br />\n根據《Xianggang01》報導，昨日下午3點左右，示威者走出梳士巴利道，部分人包圍防暴警察投擲雜物，遭警方以胡椒噴霧與手投式催淚彈反擊，隨後增援的警方到場，連開多發催淚彈，現場煙霧瀰漫，煙霧隨風飄到半島酒店附近，引起在外圍觀民眾和旅客身體不適，許多人逃到半島酒店大廳避難，半島酒店的工作人員也未加阻止。事後避難者一一離開後，半島酒店才關閉所有出入口，安排保安駐守，並稱僅供住客進出。<br />\n<br />\n臉書專頁「昔日香港」表示，這是香港酒店歷史性的第二次開放給民眾，成立於1928年的半島酒店，二戰期間曾被日軍徵收為臨時總部，1942年以「東亞酒店」名義重開接待客人，同時也成了2萬名猶太難民的避難所，當時這些難民以香港為轉運站，申請轉赴美國、澳洲或歐洲的簽證，當時半島酒店的經營者Lawrence毅然敞開半島酒店大門，收留這些無家可歸的難民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HMJQMWjFVXdeqzY341tqsA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD05MzEuNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ajnzuN2pBXEKUNBu5huG7Q--~B/aD02MDA7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/4e11e61aa3019141236278282372f844\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHMJQMWjFVXdeqzY341tqsA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD05MzEuNQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FajnzuN2pBXEKUNBu5huG7Q--~B%2FaD02MDA7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2F4e11e61aa3019141236278282372f844&h=3c024c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港近來形成一股「懲罰黃店」的潮流，指支持示威的香港人會特意到支持抗爭的店家，以消費來「懲罰」。香港藝人杜汶澤臉書專頁「杜汶澤 喱騷 Chapman To&rsquo;s late show」幽默稱香港半島酒店是「懲罰成本最高的黃店」，不過半島酒店創辦人嘉道理家族是香港中電最大股東，因此準時繳電費也是一種支持。<br />\n<br />\n半島酒店為香港最古老的酒店，最便宜的房型每晚要價至少新台幣15,000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B3%B6%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E9%81%BF%E9%9B%A3-031425976.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%25AC%25A1-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E9%2581%25BF%25E9%259B%25A3-031425976.html&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD54tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=44c57521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B3%B6%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E9%81%BF%E9%9B%A3-031425976.html</a>"},{"pid":"170dbb12e03b8e404c4ea962f2abd38e48e31258","tid":1679064,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3d9dbc1390b318d774cd656f4c9c18384a5852c7","tid":1679064,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":